Software needed:
	- Either Ubuntu or OS X
		* OS X needs fink installed
			* As a rule, we use python easy_install for python modules that don't have external requirements
		
	- SciPy python module
		- Ubuntu 
			> sudo apt-get install python-scipy
		- OS X 
			> fink install scipy-py27

			* Needs main/unstable branch ; see http://www.finkproject.org/faq/usage-fink.php#unstable 
			  >>>> TURN OFF UNSTABLE WHEN COMPLETED!! <<<<

	- Haskell
		- Ubuntu
			> sudo apt-get install python-scipy python-numpy python-matplotlib ghc
		- OS X 
			> fink install ghc

	- MatPlotLib python module
		- Ubuntu
			> sudo apt-get install python-matplotlib
		- OS X
			> sudo easy_install matplotlib

	- Cluster python module
		- Ubuntu
			> sudo apt-get install python-cluster
		- OS X
			> sudo easy_install cluster

	- Basemap python module
		- Ubuntu 
			> sudo apt-get install libgeos-dev
			> sudo pip install http://sourceforge.net/projects/matplotlib/files/matplotlib-toolkits/basemap-1.0.1/basemap-1.0.1.tar.gz/download

		- OS X
			> fink install libgeos2
			> sudo env GEOS_DIR=/sw easy_install install cluster http://sourceforge.net/projects/matplotlib/files/matplotlib-toolkits/basemap-1.0.1/basemap-1.0.1.tar.gz/download
